{"tid":1611954,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"見到啲偽勇武急急腳del ig story真係好笑","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T06:15:38.000Z","uid":25133,"like":30,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f19467166709630cc28efd6575fc61a03ea787ab","tid":1611954,"uid":25133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"非分化<br />\n但我屌你班<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>偽勇武</strong></span>呀<br />\n出到去著晒gear但咩都唔做<br />\n剩係識行去前線影相post ig拎光環<br />\n以為而家cosplay event呀？<br />\n琴日一話暴動就個個驚撚到仆街狗沖del story<br />\n根本得你班偽勇武要驚<br />\n真前線既手足平時根本就知唔應該打卡攞屎上身<br />\n係得你地先會咁心急明明咩都無做<br />\n但就上前線影張相扮有貢獻<br />\n<br />\n好屌完 最後真心同呢班手足講<br />\nDllm出到黎就唔該你做野啦<br />\n而家係革命呀 唔係出show<br />\n無論你係咩崗位 前線定和理非<br />\n真心多謝你肯企出黎<br />\n但麻煩你諗清楚自己屬於邊到<br />\n唔好拎住和理非既心態<br />\n但又拎晒人地既gear企前面阻住晒<br />\n當然各位手足都希望大家可以覺醒<br />\n上齊裝係前面一齊努力"},{"pid":"9e7403a87cc6cfe18934ae38099201458a14c356","tid":1611954,"uid":170594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f09637fcd395e974b8f9aeb98335ecfb6bc7bb","tid":1611954,"uid":25133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318e96ec92d36b192ccc3379193a14b608fe4901","tid":1611954,"uid":267937,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c5721e548d5c0965bd31213af9868555f57fd2c","tid":1611954,"uid":25133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95c2b18a1859c25c17de05936a0bb9e90d2f488","tid":1611954,"uid":40061,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:03:50.000Z","msg":"又分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faca05ba0dcda1b489b4